{"ts": "2026-06-08T23:45:33.752224+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 14e35346190d0ff04ea56d634a34dbac593ed1c9)", "id": "lc_df78d4d5-6b73-4892-8663-eefb74cd767b"}, {"type": "text", "text": "{\n  \"name\": \"vue3-vite-starter-template\",\n  \"description\": \"Vue.js 3 Vite starter template with Pinia, Vue Router, Bootstrap and more.\",\n  \"version\": \"0.0.0-semantic-release\",\n  \"license\": \"MIT\",\n  \"repository\": \"https://github.com/kouts/vue3-vite-starter-template\",\n  \"packageManager\": \"pnpm@10.20.0\",\n  \"type\": \"module\",\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"preinstall\": \"npx only-allow pnpm\",\n    \"dev\": \"vite\",\n    \"build\": \"vite build\",\n    \"preview\": \"vite preview\",\n    \"build-preview\": \"vite build && vite preview\",\n    \"lint\": \"eslint \\\"**/*.{vue,ts,js}\\\"\",\n    \"lint-fix\": \"eslint --fix \\\"**/*.{vue,ts,js}\\\"\",\n    \"test:unit\": \"vitest\",\n    \"test:unit-coverage\": \"vitest run --coverage\",\n    \"prepare\": \"husky\"\n  },\n  \"dependencies\": {\n    \"bootstrap\": \"^5.3.8\",\n    \"jsdom\": \"^27.1.0\",\n    \"pinia\": \"^3.0.3\",\n    \"vitest\": \"^4.0.6\",\n    \"vue\": \"^3.5.22\",\n    \"vue-router\": \"^4.6.3\"\n  },\n  \"devDependencies\": {\n    \"@commitlint/cli\": \"^20.1.0\",\n    \"@commitlint/config-conventional\": \"^20.0.0\",\n    \"@fullhuman/postcss-purgecss\": \"^7.0.2\",\n    \"@fullhuman/vue-cli-plugin-purgecss\": \"^7.0.2\",\n    \"@kouts/eslint-config\": \"^3.0.9\",\n    \"@vitejs/plugin-vue\": \"^6.0.1\",\n    \"@vue/compiler-sfc\": \"^3.5.22\",\n    \"@vue/test-utils\": \"^2.4.6\",\n    \"autoprefixer\": \"^10.4.21\",\n    \"eslint\": \"^9.39.0\",\n    \"husky\": \"^9.1.7\",\n    \"lint-staged\": \"^16.2.6\",\n    \"prettier\": \"^3.6.2\",\n    \"sass\": \"^1.93.3\",\n    \"vite\": \"^7.1.12\",\n    \"vite-plugin-html\": \"^3.2.2\"\n  }\n}", "id": "lc_c890e6fc-591d-4fed-ac6c-8d85a59a1f45"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "c8b61f6f-b07c-4f3e-b141-6965ce4cfe3a", "tool_call_id": "call_c136898fe8a549819e830d97", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-08T23:45:33.940138+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 14cdb62b2e100f4ebf75f88cf5c58669437208e3)", "id": "lc_2904af14-5dba-4e12-b527-707ae228cfc3"}, {"type": "text", "text": "# vue3-vite-starter-template\n\nA single page app [Vite](https://vitejs.dev) starter template, created to easily bootstrap Vue.js 3 apps.\n\n**Features**\n\n- Vitest for unit testing\n- Pinia for state management\n- Vue Router 4 for client-side routing\n- Bootstrap 5.3 for layout and styling\n- SCSS variables inside Vue components\n- Purgecss for eliminating unused CSS\n- Basic multiple layouts feature\n- ESLint config based on `eslint:recommended` with sensible defaults :relaxed:\n- [Prettier](https://prettier.io/) for code formatting\n- Automated release workflow with [semantic-release](https://github.com/semantic-release/semantic-release)\n\n## Project setup\n\n```\npnpm install\n```\n\n### Compiles and hot-reloads for development\n\n```\npnpm run dev\n```\n\n### Compiles and minifies for production\n\n```\npnpm run build\n```\n\n## Run your unit tests\n\n```\npnpm run test:unit\n```\n\n### Lints files\n\n```\npnpm run lint\n```\n\n### Lints and fixes files\n\n```\nnpm run lint-fix\n```\n\n### Customize configuration\n\nSee [Configuration Reference](https://vitejs.dev/guide/).\n", "id": "lc_3d31cde4-1293-40f8-9b2f-b94210b98bf2"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "5943cf30-947a-4f4f-9586-4e88a25dfddc", "tool_call_id": "call_c430055e3dc54aef95689e76", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-08T23:45:43.054078+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "Here are the **setup and day-to-day development commands** for this repo, taken from **`README.md`** and the **`scripts` in `package.json`**.\n\n### Install dependencies\n```bash\npnpm install\n```\n\n### Start dev server (hot-reload)\n```bash\npnpm dev\n```\n\n### Build for production\n```bash\npnpm build\n```\n\n### Preview production build\n```bash\npnpm preview\n```\nOr build + preview in one step:\n```bash\npnpm build-preview\n```\n\n### Run unit tests\n```bash\npnpm test:unit\n```\n\n### Run unit tests with coverage\n```bash\npnpm test:unit-coverage\n```\n\n### Lint\n```bash\npnpm lint\n```\n\n### Lint + auto-fix\n```bash\npnpm lint-fix\n```\n\nIf you want, I can also check the repo’s **Node version target** (e.g., `.nvmrc`) and whether **Husky/lint-staged** are wired up in the repo.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 307, "prompt_tokens": 5315, "total_tokens": 5622, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 81, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 4224, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.0007568814, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 0.0004897914, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.00026709}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-pro-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780962334-gA7NjLZf2BDvFDVGZOWs", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea9a0-94f4-7e92-9c29-a723abf857d9-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 5315, "output_tokens": 307, "total_tokens": 5622, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 4224}, "output_